{"id":573630,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/12/水替士心｜清华教授学术造假抄袭日本弓道，炮制/","date":"2017-12-02T06:40:32Z","modified":"2017-12-02T06:40:32Z","title":"水替士心｜清华教授学术造假抄袭日本弓道，炮制伪传统","content":"<p>2016年11月，由清华大学历史系彭林教授主持的2014年度国家社科基金重大项目《〈仪礼〉复原与当代日常礼仪重建研究》的阶段性成果《乡射礼》实验性复原的拍摄完成，并于同年9月，彭林、韩冰雪主编出版了《礼射初阶》一书。</p>\n<p>翻开《礼射初阶》，我深深地惊讶了。书中有多达二十多处对日本弓道教材的抄袭，对日本弓道技术及礼仪的模仿是令人惊讶的明目张胆。然而比仿日本弓道更糟糕的，是在清华《乡射礼》短片中体现出来的僵尸般反人性又没有历史依据的动作姿态，这是对周代《仪礼》的故意歪曲和丑化。清华这样一座全国最著名的理工学府，居然出现这种伪传统幺蛾子，实在是匪夷所思。彭林等人，拿着国家社科基金做出的研究成果，就是个山寨版日本弓道；并且将其在全国高校中推广蔓延，用他反智反人性的<span style=\"color: #ff8a78;\"><b><span style=\"color: #d24a35;\">伪传统</span></b></span>“礼义”教学理念毒害全国各地的学生。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1eqv6k53j20e80oigpv.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573631\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1eqv6k53j20e80oigpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"818\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1eqv6k53j20e80oigpv.jpg 512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1eqv6k53j20e80oigpv-174x300.jpg 174w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>日式服装，日式正坐，日式射法八节，这就是中国礼射？</b></p>\n<p>《礼射初阶》主要抄袭的是一本台湾出版的《弓道》，这也是唯一一本中文的日本弓道正规刊物。此书在国内网盘有资源，<span style=\"color: #333333;\"><b>很容易下载到</b></span>。翻开这两本书目录就明显发现，两书在结构上都非常雷同。下文中对比的图片，简体中文彩图的是《礼射初阶》，繁体中文黑白图的是《弓道》。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjec9mj20rs0ks7a6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573633\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjec9mj20rs0ks7a6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjec9mj20rs0ks7a6.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjec9mj20rs0ks7a6-300x224.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjec9mj20rs0ks7a6-768x574.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_573632\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjdsmhj20rs0kun1x.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-573632\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjdsmhj20rs0kun1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjdsmhj20rs0kun1x.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjdsmhj20rs0kun1x-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjdsmhj20rs0kun1x-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">两书版本信息</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_573634\" style=\"width: 485px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjjd75j20m80uhjwk.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-573634\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjjd75j20m80uhjwk.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"651\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjjd75j20m80uhjwk.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjjd75j20m80uhjwk-219x300.jpg 219w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjjd75j20m80uhjwk-768x1053.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erjjd75j20m80uhjwk-747x1024.jpg 747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">《礼射初阶》目录</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_573635\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erk1fzoj20m80wtdqt.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-573635\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erk1fzoj20m80wtdqt.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"812\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erk1fzoj20m80wtdqt.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erk1fzoj20m80wtdqt-203x300.jpg 203w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erk1fzoj20m80wtdqt-768x1134.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1erk1fzoj20m80wtdqt-694x1024.jpg 694w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">《弓道》目录</span></p></div>\n<p>​大意总结一下两书目录：</p>\n<p>《礼射初阶》：1历史 2技法 3器材 4比赛规则 5术语解释</p>\n<p>《弓道》：1历史 2技法 3器材 4练习及比赛规则 5矫正 6比赛规则 7术语解释</p>\n<p>虽然《弓道》目录章节更多，实际上从内容结构来看是完全雷同的，顺序略有不同。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1v5ptj20rs0ypjyf.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573637\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1v5ptj20rs0ypjyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"625\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1v5ptj20rs0ypjyf.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1v5ptj20rs0ypjyf-240x300.jpg 240w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1v5ptj20rs0ypjyf-768x959.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1v5ptj20rs0ypjyf-820x1024.jpg 820w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1r5fvj20m80mowjc.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573636\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1r5fvj20m80mowjc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"510\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1r5fvj20m80mowjc.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1r5fvj20m80mowjc-294x300.jpg 294w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1r5fvj20m80mowjc-768x783.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ew1r5fvj20m80mowjc-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>​技法章节，开篇就是抄袭了弓道的“八节 七道 五味 五法”叙述结构。</p>\n<p>以下抄袭，在于<span style=\"color: #d24a35;\"><b>叙述方式、图示方式、技术要点等</b></span>多方面的，注意图片说明</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_573638\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ewdsmhyj20rs0ajdik.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-573638\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ewdsmhyj20rs0ajdik.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"227\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ewdsmhyj20rs0ajdik.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ewdsmhyj20rs0ajdik-300x114.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1ewdsmhyj20rs0ajdik-768x291.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">站立姿势，脚距的大小</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_573640\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1exnd8b4j20rs0cpn0e.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-573640\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1exnd8b4j20rs0cpn0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1exnd8b4j20rs0cpn0e.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1exnd8b4j20rs0cpn0e-300x137.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/728b299fly1fm1exnd8b4j20rs0cpn0e-768x351.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\